n for practising teachers and trainee teachers. It will help them transform their classrooms into multilingual environments where all children have equal opportunity to participate, learn and grow.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aEducation, Bilingual. 0aImmigrant childrenxEducation. 0aLanguage and languagesxStudy and teaching. 0aMultilingual education. 0aMultilingualism. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aEAL.  aELL.  aLAP.  aLinguistically Appropriate Practice .  aTESOL.  abilingualism .  adiverse classrooms.  aemergent bilinguals .  alinguistic diversity .  amultilingual pedagogy.  amultilingual teaching.  amultilingualism.  anewcomer students .08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishz978311061030708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019z9783110606287oZDB-23-DSP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066146040uhttps://doi.org/10.21832/978178892496240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781788924962423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781788924962/original  a978-3-11-061030-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-066146-0  MultiLingual Matters Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-